verbose_text: Similarly, after combination mechanical stretch with no imatinib treatment, the protein levels of M2 and M3 were increased to 4.511 +/-0.283 and (3.573 +/-0.229, respectively (p < 0.001), whereas after combination mechanical stretch with imatinib treatment and combination no stretch with no imatinib treatment, the protein levels of M2 and M3 were 2.518 +/-0.195 and 2.077 +/-0.168, and 1.308 +/-0.046 and 1.242 +/-0.052, respectively, as shown in XREF_FIG.
